news.title: Ending a pandemic: How to calculate how many people need to get vaccinated for herd immunity
news.summary: Each Covid-19 vaccine offers a different level of protection. This means that the number of people who need to be vaccinated in order to stop Covid-19 from spreading in the country depends on which jab is used.
